But you have not directed it,
Miss
.
There is no
necessity
for directing it. Do you
deliver
it to the
person
who gave it to your care.
Ah!
Miss
, I think you will repent, for Le Brun
tells me Sir George loves you to
distraction
. He has
been walking in the garden
these
three hours in hopes
of meeting with you.
I am
vastly
