.
But you do not pity him, though his heart is
almost
breaking!
I do pity him, Harley, indeed, I do; and if he
were poorer, and I were richer.
Ah!
Miss
, Love levels all
distinctions
. Sir George
would think
himself
the
person
obliged. He told Le
Brun you were the only woman he ever thought on with
partiality.
Mrs. Harley,
said
Rebecca, opening a drawer
of a
small
