Ponsonville
;and
how old are you?
Four years
last
Christmas
.
Jenny, cried he, taking hold of her hand. Jenny,
my love, how like a villain I have behaved to this boy
and you.
He drew her towards him with one hand, while
he embraced the child with the other. She
