. Lord
Melvin called to inquire for his boy,he heard the
tidings
,
and never
rested
till he
discovered
our place of
retreat.
Miserable
indeed was the apartment where he
found his Jenny. He offered her independence for
herself
,
her mother, and children. I
blush
to add the
remainder
,
but let no one
boast
their virtue till the cold hand
of poverty has tried its
