, has had a very
disagreeable
time in America. I dare
say
you are happy to find
yourself
in England again.
Sincerely
so
, Madam.
This thought Rebecca, is undoubtedly a daughter.
The Colonel mentions,
resumed
the Lady, that
you would
wish
to engage as companion to an elderly
Lady, or as
governess
to
some
genteel family of
children
.
Either
