you, my adorable girl? I
have found you after
such
a long
separation
, when I
thought you
lost
for ever, and we will never part
again.
For heaven's
sake
let me go Sir George. Why
am I thus detained? Are you not married?
By this time a crowd had gathered round them. An
old
sailor
seeing
a woman in
distress
rushed
