Will you buy the gold, Sir?
said
Rebecca.
No, cried the Lady, he
shall
not buy it. If
you will not part with it altogether to me for twice its
value, (I am certain you will pardon the remark) but
one motive could lead you to
wish
to
dispose
of the
setting
.
As
