she
is an amiable woman,
and may prove a valuable friend.
Lady Chatterton,
said
Rebecca, reading the card.
Yes, continued he,
she
was Lady Eleanor
Harcourt
,
only daughter of the late Earl. She has been
married about three years. A
most
