As my Lady is not at home, my dear
Miss
Ossiter
,
said
she
, I will call again another time.
Well, then, let it be
soon
, my own Rebecca;
say
you will come again to-morrow.
Rebecca tenderly embraced the affectionate child, and
having given her a kind of half
promise
to
see
her
soon
again,
hastily
left the
house
.
Every thing,
said
she
,
conspires
against
me. I
never find a friend but
some
cross
